Package org.vectorbase.gdav

Class Summary
ConfigInfo reads all relevant information from the optional (config.xml) config file stores this information and provides accessor classes for this and other information.
DisplayServlet Deprecated. As of release 1.0, replaced by GdavServlet
GdavServlet the main servlet, receives initial request from user, sets up connections to the DB and provides a simple search function.
ServletInfo reads all relevant information from the compulsory (gdav.xml) config file stores this information and provides accessor classes for this and other information.
